\c 10
\s Vanakomana vaJafeti, naHamu naShemu
\p
\v 1 Zvino awa marudzi evanakomana vaNowa, Shemu, Hamu, naJa­feti; ivo vakaberekerwa vana shure kwe­mvura zhinji.
\p
\v 2 Vanakomana vaJafeti: Gomeru, naMagogi, naMadhai naJavhani naTubhari naMisheki, naTirasi.
\v 3 Zvino vanakomana vaGomeru: Ashikenazi naRifati naTogarima.
\v 4 Nevanakomana vaJavhani: Erisha naTashisi naKi­timi naDhodhanimu.
\v 5 Nezviwi izvi zvechirudzi zvakagoverwa munyika dzavo umwe neumwe nerurimi rwake, ne­mhuri dzavo, nendudzi dzavo.
\p
\v 6 Nevanakomana vaHamu: Kushi naMiziraimu naPuti naKanani.
\v 7 Uye vanakomana vaKushi: Sebha naHa­vhira naSabhata naRama naSabhuteka. Nevanakomana vaRama: Shebha naDhedhani.
\v 8 Kushi akabereka Nimurodhi, ndiye akatanga kuva une simba pa­nyika.
\v 9 Waiva mudzinganisi une simba pamberi paJehovha; naizvozvo vanoti: SaNimurodhi, mudzinganisi une simba pa­mberi paJehovha.
\v 10 Uye mavambo eushe hwake aiva paBhabheri neEreki neAkadhi neKarine panyika yeShinari.
\v 11 Akabuda kunyika iyo, akaenda Asiria, ndokuvaka Ninivhe neRohobhoti-iri neKara,
\v 12 neRe­seni pakati peNinivhe neKara (iri iguta guru).
\v 13 Zvino Miziraimu akabereka vaRudhi nevaAnami nevaRehabhi nevaNafituhimu,
\v 14 nevaPaturusi nevaKasiruhi (kwakabva kwaari vaFirisitia) nevaKafutori.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Kanani wakabereka Sidhoni, dangwe rake, naHeti;
\v 16 nevaJebhusi ne­vaAmori, nevaGirigashi;
\v 17 nevaHivhi, nevaAriki, nevaSini,
\v 18 nevaArivhadhi, nevaZemari, nevaHamati. Shure kwai­vava nemhuri dzevaKanani dzakapararira.
\p
\v 19 Zvino muganhu wavaKanani wakabva paSidhoni ukaenda Gerari kusvika Gaza, uchienda Sodhoma neGomora neAdhamu neZibhoimu kusvika paRasha.
\p
\v 20 Ava vanakomana vaHamu, nemhuri dzavo, nendimi dzavo, munyika dzavo, nendudzi dzavo.
\p
\v 21 Naiye Shemu, baba vevana vose vaEbheru, mukuru waJafeti wakabereke­rwa vana.
\v 22 Vanakomana vaShemu: Eramu naAshuri, naAripakisha­dhi naRudhi naAramu.
\v 23 Uye vanakomana vaAramu: Uzi naHuri naGeteri naMashi.
\v 24 Zvino Aripakishadhi wakabereka Shera, Shera ndokubereka Ebheri.
\v 25 Ebheru ndokuberekerwa vanakomana vaviri, zita reumwe \add raiva\add* Peregi, nekuti pamazuva ake nyika yakakamurwa; uye zita remunun'una wake \add raiva\add* Jokitani.
\v 26 Jokitani ndokubereka Arimodhadhi naSherefi naHazarimavheti naJera
\v 27 naHadhoramu naUsari naDhikira
\v 28 naObhari naAbhimaeri naShebha
\v 29 naOfiri naHavhira naJobhabhu; ava vose \add vaiva\add* vanakomana vaJokitani.
\v 30 Ugaro hwavo hwaitangira paMesha kuenda Sefari, gomo rekumabvazuva.
\v 31 Ava vanakomana vaShemu, nemhuri dzavo nendimi dzavo munyika dzavo, nendudzi dzavo.
\p
\v 32 Ava \add i\add*mhuri dzevanakomana vaNowa, nemazera avo nendudzi dzavo; kwavari kwakaparadzaniswa ndudzi dzose shure kwemvura zhinji.
